title: Nuance_PaperPort_14.5.13264.1829_Professional_With_Keygen
description:
Nuance PaperPort 14.5 Professional v14.5.13264.1829 With Serial # Keygen - This is Company Install - All you need is the serial # to install
Also Patch1 - From Paperport Software Update (Included here) takes it to v14.5.15168.1450

Once Installed you will see the software update manager tell you there is a PATCH1 - I included here or you can download it from the Update Manager & it will work fine.

I have tried many document management programs but as of 10/20/2015 this is one of the best.  You can view your files & manage files quickly.

Powerful 100-percent industry-standard PDF creation and editing
Fast, professional, and productive scanning made easy from any device
Store and share documents on the network, in Microsoft SharePoint, or in the cloud
Get organized and find files, documents, and photos--instantly
Anywhere-anytime access to your files using iPhone, iPad, or Android

INTALLATION:

1.  If you already have PaperPort Installed then go to add/remove/uninstall programs and remove "PaperPort Image Printer 64-bit".  This new 14.5 will automatically uninstall the older versions.

2.  Now run the keygen.exe - you only need the serial # from this - without the serial PaperPort will install but will not work.  Copy the serial and close the keygen.

3.  Now run PaperPort_14.5_Professional.exe (This is the origional PaperPort program).  Or you can exctract this EXE and then run AUTORUN.EXE

4.  It will ask you for a name and company name - enter anything you want.

5.  Also the 3rd box is for the serial # you generated above - enter it.

This installs Nuance PDF Create 7 and Nuance PDF Viewer Plus - you can manually uninstall these programs later if you do not want them - I usually uninstall the "Nuance PDF Viewer Plus" as I already have Adobe Acrobat Writer that does more but if you do not have another PDF manager (not talking about a reader) then leave these as they will be useful to you
